    "type": "message",
    "text": "I am excited to be there. Of note, I forgot to link any information about the Lean Coffee[1] meeting method that I feel would work really well for this group. The link goes into more depth then what we typically do internally at Reaktor when having a community of practice meeting. The simple method.\n\n1. [5 mins] Personal brainstorming ideas writing to notes\n2. Everyone sticks there notes into a big pile\n3. A topic is selected as a group\n4. [10 mins] Group discussion on topic\n5. goto 3\n\nIts simple, yet effective at creating well balanced group discussions. I’m not trying to dictate this as our method, just trying to share. I am open to other types of facilitation methods!\n\n[1] <http://agilecoffee.com/leancoffee/>",
